  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="info-box">
          <div class="jumbotron">
            <h1>Welcome Doctor</h1>
            <hr>
            <h5>Here are some functionalities available to you, which helps you to fetch the appoinment of patients.</h5>
            <hr>
            <h4>The Appoinment Button</h4>
            <h5>It allows you to see all the appoinment that are accepted by you and view the details of the patients that you are going to 
              treat on the following details provided to you and there is also a "Done" button which helps you to move the treated patient 
              details to your previous patient records.
            </h5>
            <hr>
            <h4>Your Profile Button</h4>
            <h5>It allows you to see all the details of yourself and you can see and update all of your details for further future purpose.
            </h5>
            <hr>
            <h4>Records Button</h4>
            <h5>It allows you to see the number of patients that you have treated in the past and if any other patient comes to you after some
              days, then you are able to view the record of that patient.
            </h5>
            <hr>
            <h4>All Request Button</h4>
            <h5>This button allow you to see all the patient that want appoinment from you, It allow you to either accept or reject the patient 
              appoinment according to your choice and according to your convenience.
            </h5>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
